<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <%- include('bootstrap') %>
        <style>
            body {
                display: flex;
                min-height: 100vh;
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .content {
                flex-grow: 1;
            }

            .iframe-container {
                max-width: 560px;
                aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
            }

            /* Then style the iframe to fit in the container div with full height and width */
            .responsive-iframe {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
            }
        </style>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('navbar') %>
        <div class="container content mt-3 mb-3">
            <h1>Volunteering</h1>
            <div class="accordion mt-3" id="accordionExample">
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed shadow-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                            Capital One Coder Mentor
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><b>Capital One Coders : 6/28/22 - 7/7/22</b></p>
                            <p>
                                I taught middle school students build their own website using HTML and CSS. We used <a
                                    href="https://glitch.com/" class="link-primary" target="_blank">Glitch</a> in order
                                to create the websites. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed shadow-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                            Christ's Kitchen Volunteer
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><b>Christ's Kitchen : 1/20</b></p>
                            <p>
                                I helped cook & serve free meals to over 300 individuals. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed shadow-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                            Promise Pointe Volunteer
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><b>Promise Pointe : 12/19 - 1/20, 12/20</b></p>
                            <p>
                                During the winter break of 2019, I caulked the walls and roof of a house that would
                                eventually be inhabited by a formerly homeless individual. During the winter break of
                                2020, I painted a forest mural on a 40 by 8 feet storage container for Promise
                                Pointe, a residential community organization for the formerly homeless of the Victoria
                                area. I spent a total of 61 hours painting this mural. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="accordion-item">
                    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                        <button class="accordion-button collapsed shadow-none" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                            data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                            Vitality Court Volunteer
                        </button>
                    </h2>
                    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                        data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
                        <div class="accordion-body">
                            <p><b>Vitality Court - Assisted Living community : 12/19 - 1/20</b></p>
                            <p>
                                During the winter break of 2019, I played several styles of piano music for senior
                                residents during their dinnertime. </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <%- include('footer') %>
</body>

</html>